		</ul>
	</td>
	<td>
		<ul>
			<li class="record">Four No-Hitters*</li>				
			<li>One Perfect Game</li>
			<li>MVP in 1963</li>
			<li>382 strikeouts in 1965</li>
			<li>Cy Young Award Winner 1963, 1965, 1966</li>
			<li>11 Shutouts in 1963</li>
			<li class="record"*>Two 18-strikout games</li>
		</ul>
